01:20.842 --> 01:23.564
You have 30′.

01:30.002 --> 01:33.110
I have to say,
I find this very strange.

01:33.110 --> 01:38.373
I always thought I'd be the one 
visiting you in the mental hospital.

01:39.583 --> 01:41.868
I'm excited about tomorrow.

01:41.868 --> 01:44.641
Please tell me we have a shot.

01:44.641 --> 01:46.981
I don't know how much longer
I can take it in here.

01:46.981 --> 01:48.993
We have a shot.

01:49.444 --> 01:51.316
I'll get you out.

01:51.316 --> 01:53.945
I don't need to hear it, Alan.
I need it to happen.

01:53.945 --> 01:56.013
The board will question you directly.

01:56.013 --> 01:59.853
It's entirely possible
they'll try to provoke you.

01:59.853 --> 02:01.682
To make sure I'm bombproof?

02:01.682 --> 02:04.430
Sorry? —It's an expression 
with horses.

02:04.430 --> 02:06.912
To be safe to ride, a horse 
needs to be bombproof.

02:06.912 --> 02:08.095
It doesn't spook easily.

02:08.095 --> 02:11.684
Can't have one who just flies off.

02:11.684 --> 02:13.677
Yes, in addition to not flying off,

02:13.677 --> 02:15.109
you need to show contrition.

02:15.109 --> 02:19.856
They like to see that you're sorry.

02:19.856 --> 02:21.519
I am.

02:23.189 --> 02:26.866
I, I am so sorry,

02:26.866 --> 02:30.515
so deep, deeply ashamed.

02:30.515 --> 02:32.529
How do I say it right?

02:32.529 --> 02:34.529
Just like that.

02:36.931 --> 02:37.947
Christine,

02:37.947 --> 02:40.518
you were in love with 
a man who was unworthy of you,

02:40.518 --> 02:44.286
who made you doubt everything
that you had a right to count on,

02:44.286 --> 02:47.696
who perhaps even toyed with your sanity.

02:47.696 --> 02:51.187
Still no excuse for trying to kill him.

02:51.187 --> 02:54.192
Perhaps he had it coming.

02:55.417 --> 02:57.791
Perhaps you did.

